Install instructions
--------------------

# !!! still under heavy development.

Requirements:
- CMake & make
- a C++ compiler
- ncurses
- openssl v1.0.0+
- glibc 2.9+

For Ubuntu 12.04 LTS run:
 sudo apt-get install cmake make g++ libncurses5-dev libssl-dev

For RHEL6.4 run:
 sudo yum install cmake gcc-c++ ncurses-devel openssl-devel


To build & run x509ls:
----------------------

 mkdir build
 cd build

 cmake ../
 make

 x509ls/x509ls


To install:
-----------

 sudo make install

